column15: body_text:"You find a shimmering mass of light encompassing the center of the room.   Its warm glow and enchanting patterns invite you in."
column18: text:"[Enter] Upgrade 2 random cards. Lose 16 HP."

column14: body_text:"As you walk through the light
column15: you notice that the light is absorbed into you.  It\u0027s scorching hot ! However
column16: the pain quickly recedes.  You feel invigorated
column17: as though you received a well deserved slap."

column16: body_text:"Before you lies an elaborate shrine to an ancient spirit. "
column23: text:"[Desecrate] Gain 275 Gold. Become Cursed - Regret."

column14: body_text:"As your hand touches the shrine
column15: gold rains from the ceiling showering you in riches. "
body_text:"You fall into a puddle.  IT\u0027S MADE OF SLIME GOOP!!  Frantically
column16: you claw yourself out over several minutes as you feel the goop starting to burn.  You can feel goop in your ears
column19: you notice that some of your gold is missing. Looking back to the puddle you see your missing coins combined with gold from unfortunate adventurers mixed together in the puddle."
column22: text:"[Gather Gold] Gain 75 Gold. Lose 11 HP."

column14: body_text:"Feeling the sting of the goop as the prolonged exposure starts to melt away at your skin
column15: you manage to fish out the gold."
body_text:"You enter a corridor full of hypnotizing colored mushrooms.  Due to your lack of specialization in mycology you are unable to identify the specimens.  You want to escape
column16: but feel oddly compelled to eat a mushroom..."
column23: text:"[Eat] Heal 20 HP. Become Cursed - Parasite."

column14: body_text:"Ambushed!!  Rodents infested by the mushrooms appear out of nowhere!"
